---item_29 Corrupted Wyld Luck---
Type :: Usable
Icon :: items_645
Slot :: Item
Rarity :: Legendary
Max Stacks :: 99

Use this item to get another loot box from the boss you just killed. Must be used quickly after the boss dies or will not function. Can be used in Corrupted Dungeons up to Level 5.

A lot of research went into the anti-Corruption Coating to let this work in places where the Ethos Corruption has spread.